      <memberdef kind="define" id="group__b12__interface_1ga5ebbce02f5cb47de4565ef17d57ca25a" prot="public" static="no">
        <name>BC12_CHARGER_MIN_CURR_UA</name>
        <initializer>2500</initializer>
        <briefdescription>
<para>BC1.2 USB charger minimum current. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Set to match the Isusp of 2.5 mA parameter. This is returned by the driver when either BC1.2 detection fails, or the attached partner is a SDP (standard downstream port).</para>
<para>The application may increase the current draw after determining the USB device state of suspended/unconfigured/configured. Suspended: 2.5 mA Unconfigured: 100 mA Configured: 500 mA (USB 2.0) </para>
        </detaileddescription>
        <inbodydescription>
